videos.description: Maryland's Bruno Fernando misses the slam at one end, then Nebraska's Isaiah Roby dunks in Jalen Smith's face for the huge flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maryland's missed dunk sets up Nebraska's poster slam) 2019/01/02

videos.headline: Maryland's missed dunk sets up Nebraska's poster slam

videos.description: Anthony Cowan Jr. throws one over the top to Jalen Smith who dunks it plus the foul.
videos.headline: Smith gets huge and-1 dunk for Maryland

videos.description: Jalen Smith sinks the one-handed floater with 3.8 seconds left to lift the Terrapins past the Cornhuskers.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith's floater wins it for Maryland) 2019/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith's floater wins it for Maryland
